

=Bio=

"Davie Philip currently manages the Community Resilience Programme that developed out of the Community Powerdown Programme in 2010. Based in Cloughjordan the Community Resilience programme develops resources and delivers training in community resilience - the capability of communities to hold together, learn, adapt and maintain their ability to function in response to change."
(http://www.cultivate.ie/about-cultivate-new/our-people/1207-davie-philip)

